u with things like:\n- understanding symptoms\n- organizing what to monitor\n- interpreting preliminary tool outputs\n- preparing for a clinician visit\n- flagging when something sounds urgent\n\nIf you want, I can also explain:\n1. **what I can do**\n2. **what I can’t do**\n3. **how I make decisions**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07f43da73eaf87710169b1973ba6dc819198d313130c0d8bd5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":8285,"output":239,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8524,"cost":{"input":0.020712500000000002,"output":0.003585,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.024297500000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773246264546}}
